","data":{"biography":"Zach McGowan was born and raised in New York City, where he started acting at an early age in school productions. His passion for the stage followed him through his high school and college years and landed him on the New York City stage in 2003 where he honed his craft in numerous off Broadway productions. In 2005 Zach moved to Los Angeles to work in film and Television. Zach's film work includes \"Terminator Salvation\" directed by McG \"The Hunt For Eagle One\" (Sony Screen Gems) directed by Brian Clyde, \"Crash Point\" (Sony Screen Gems) directed by Henry Crum, and \"Seal Team Six\" directed by Mark Andrews. On Television Zach Guest-starred in the premiere episode of the 5th season of \"Numb3rs\", and in season 7 episode 6 of \"CSI Miami.\" Zach's short film work includes leading roles in \"The 14th Morning\" (LA International Short Film Festival, New Haven Film Festival, and The Method Festival), and \"Sadiq\" (official 2006 MTVU Student Film Maker Award Nominee, and winner \"Best Short\" at the San Luis Obispo International Film Festival) by Sean Mullin. Zach can also be heard in numerous advertisements, video games, and animation projects doing Voice Over work. Zach lives in Los Angeles and is a member of both SAG and AFTRA.","name":"Zach McGowan","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"NL","iso_639_1":"nl","name":"Nederlands","english_name":"Dutch","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Зак Макгоуэн","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"扎克·麦高恩 （Zach McGowan） 在纽约市出生和长大，在那里他很小的时候就开始在学校制作中表演。他对舞台的热情伴随着他度过了高中和大学时代，并于 2003 年登上了纽约市的舞台，在那里他在众多非百老汇作品中磨练了自己的手艺。2005年，扎克搬到洛杉矶从事电影和电视工作。扎克的电影作品包括麦格执导的《终结者救赎》、布莱恩·克莱德执导的《猎鹰一号》（Sony Screen Gems）、亨利·克鲁姆执导的《崩溃点》（Sony Screen Gems）、马克·安德鲁斯执导的《海豹突击队六人组》。在电视上，扎克客串出演了“Numb3rs”第 5 季的首播集，以及“CSI Miami”的第 7 季第 6 集。扎克的短片作品包括在肖恩·穆林（Sean Mullin）的《第14个早晨》（洛杉矶国际短片电影节、纽黑文电影节和方法节）和《萨迪克》（2006年MTVU学生电影制作人奖官方提名，以及圣路易斯奥比斯波国际电影节“最佳短片”奖得主）中担任主角。在众多广告、视频游戏和动画项目中也可以听到 Zach 的配音工作。扎克住在洛杉矶，是SAG和AFTRA的成员。","name":"扎克·麦高恩","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"紮克·麥高恩 （Zach McGowan） 在紐約市出生和長大，在那裏他很小的時候就開始在學校製作中表演。他對舞台的熱情伴隨著他度過了高中和大學時代，並於 2003 年登上了紐約市的舞台，在那裏他在眾多非百老匯作品中磨練了自己的手藝。2005 年，紮克搬到洛杉磯從事電影和電視工作。紮克的電影作品包括麥格執導的《未來戰士救贖》、布萊恩·克萊德執導的《獵鷹一號》（Sony Screen Gems）、亨利·克魯姆執導的《崩潰點》（Sony Screen Gems）、馬克·安德魯斯執導的《海豹突擊隊六人組》。在電視上，紮克客串出演了“Numb3rs”第 5 季的首播集，以及“CSI Miami”的第 7 季第 6 集。紮克的短片作品包括在肖恩·穆林（Sean Mullin）的《第 14 個早晨》（洛杉磯國際短片電影節、紐黑文電影節和方法節）和《薩迪克》（2006 年 MTVU 學生電影製作人獎官方提名，以及聖路易斯奧比斯波國際電影節“最佳短片”獎得主）中擔任主角。在眾多廣告、視頻遊戲和動畫項目中也可以聽到 Zach 的配音工作。紮克住在洛杉磯，是 SAG 和 AFTRA 的成員。","name":"紮克·麥高恩","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"זאק מקגוואן","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TR","iso_639_1":"tr","name":"Türkçe","english_name":"Turkish","data":{"biography":"Zachary Brendan McGowan, 5 Mayıs 1980 tarihinde New York City, ABD'de dünyaya gelmiştir. İrlanda, Rus ve Yahudi kökenli bir ailenin en küçük oğlu olan McGowan, Manhattan'da büyüdü. Babasının eski bir Birleşik Devletler Deniz Piyadesi olması ve annesinin United Airlines'da çalışması, onun disiplinli ve dünyayı tanıyan bir vizyonla yetişmesini sağladı. Okul yıllarında başarılı bir sporcu olan McGowan, futbol ve buz hokeyi takımlarında kaptanlık yaptı, ayrıca boks ve jiu-jitsu gibi dövüş sanatlarıyla ilgilendi. Eğitimini Minnesota'daki Carleton College'da tamamladıktan sonra New York'a dönerek sahne sanatlarına yöneldi.\n\nKariyerine oyunculuktan ziyade seslendirme sanatçısı olarak hızlı bir giriş yaptı. Derin, pürüzlü ve karakteristik sesi sayesinde yüzlerce film fragmanında, reklamda ve \"Iron Man\" gibi video oyunlarında seslendirme yaptı. Ekran önündeki ilk ciddi deneyimlerini \"CSI: Miami\" ve \"Numb3rs\" gibi dizilerdeki küçük rollerle kazandı. Ancak onu izleyiciyle tanıştıran ilk büyük proje, Amerikan uyarlaması \"Shameless\" (2012-2013) dizisi oldu. Burada canlandırdığı Jody Silverman karakteri, başlangıçta tek boyutlu bir figür gibi görünse de McGowan'ın komedi zamanlaması ve fiziksel performansı sayesinde dizinin en renkli karakterlerinden birine dönüştü.\n\nZach McGowan'ın kariyerindeki asıl dönüm noktası ve onu dünya çapında bir aksiyon yıldızı statüsüne taşıyan yapım, Starz kanalının korsan draması \"Black Sails\" (2014-2016) oldu. Tarihsel bir figür olan Kaptan Charles Vane'i canlandırdığı bu dizide, karakterin vahşi, tavizsiz ve özgürlüğüne düşkün yapısını mükemmel bir şekilde yansıttı. Kaslı fiziği, dövüş sahnelerindeki ustalığı ve kendine has karizmasıyla Vane'i, dizinin en popüler anti-kahramanı haline getirdi. Özellikle Eleanor Guthrie ve Kaptan Flint ile olan çatışmaları, dizinin dramatik yapısının merkezinde yer aldı.\n\n\"Black Sails\"teki başarısının hemen ardından, kült bilimkurgu dizisi \"The 100\"da (2016-2017) Buz Ulusu'nun (Azgeda) Kralı Roan rolüyle ekranlara döndü. Burada da yine savaşçı, stratejik ve onurlu bir lideri canlandırarak hayran kitlesini genişletti. Ardından Marvel Sinematik Evreni'ne adım atarak \"Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.\" dizisinde (2017-2018) ana kötü karakterlerden The Superior (Anton Ivanov) rolünü üstlendi.\n\nSinemada ise genellikle aksiyon ağırlıklı serilerin devam filmlerinde başrol oynadı. \"The Scorpion King: Book of Souls\" (2018) filminde Akrep Kral Mathayus'u ve \"Death Race: Beyond Anarchy\" (2018) filminde Connor Gibson'ı canlandırdı. Yakın dönemde \"The Walking Dead\" evreninde ve çeşitli bağımsız aksiyon filmlerinde yer alan McGowan, sert mizaçlı ve fiziksel güç gerektiren rollerin aranan ismi olmaya devam etmektedir.","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"person_2718121_translations":{"at":1772691636705,"data":{"id":2718121,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Miguel Torres Umba is an actor, director, and movement specialist known for his expertise in creating and portraying physically demanding and dynamic characters. He plays Ben in the new Paramount film Primate. \"Miguel's performance is really quite incredible ... and makes Ben feel like a legitimate threat\" - Fangoria. \"Ben is practical, spectacularly crafted by Millennium FX, and played by movement specialist Miguel Torres Umba. The chimp's transformation from sweet pet to terrifying monster serves as the film's biggest asset\" - Bloody Disgusting. Miguel was born in Colombia and began training as an actor in Bogotá before specialising in corporeal mime and physical theatre in the U.K. He is also known for his longstanding collaboration with Gecko Theatre, where he has performed in productions such as the National Theatre co-production KIN, The Wedding (UK Tour), and the feature film Institute (Gecko/BBC). Miguel's one-man show, Stardust, earned critical acclaim at the Edinburgh Fringe Festival, with The Guardian noting, \"Using a mix of animation, movement, and monologue, the storytelling is beyond impressive.\" In addition to his acting work, Miguel is a leading figure in immersive theatre. He was the creative director for Rematch Live's Rumble in the Jungle and performance director for Glastonbury's Terminal 1. He spent over 12 years at Secret Cinema, where he rose from performer to creative director, contributing to iconic productions such as Moulin Rouge, Back to the Future, and Star Wars. As a director and practitioner, Miguel's creative practice is rooted in inclusivity, playfulness, and a deep commitment to exploring socio-political issues. Through his company, Umba Arts, he has produced various projects, including Latinx Youth Theatre, a platform that empowers young Latin Americans in London to celebrate their cultural identity through the performing arts.","name":"Miguel Hernando Torres Umba","primary":true}}]}},"person_229302_translations":{"at":1772691638840,"data":{"id":229302,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Ku Feng (Chinese: 谷峰, July 3 1930 - March 27, 2025) was a Hong Kong-based actor. He appeared in hundreds of films, many of which were produced by the Shaw Brothers Studio.","name":"Ku Feng","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"1930年7月3日出生，属相为马，原名陈思文，上海人，于北平就学，对唱歌甚有研究，最令人有印象的他就是他那说得不清不楚的广东乡巴音。后赴港，曾于荔园游乐场卖唱为生。1965年，正式加入邵氏公司担任基本演员，拍过一百多部影片，为著名的性格演员，演技老辣，令人折服，代表作有《新独臂刀》、《保镖》、《双侠》及《清宫大刺杀》等，常以首领人物的姿态出现在电影中。他曾以《武松》一片获第十九届台湾金马奖最佳男配角奖。一年后他再凭《待罪的女孩》卫冕同一个殊荣。另外《又见冤家》获得了金马奖最佳男配角奖提名；影片《笼民》更是引起影坛的轰动；另外在周星驰影片中的客串也是深入人心。近年来，谷峰以拍电视剧为主，但在电影《妖夜回廊》仍可见其精采演出，还客串了《宝贝计划》中成龙的父亲。","name":"谷峰","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"谷峰","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"곡봉","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"1930 年 7 月 3 日出生，屬相為馬，原名谷峰，上海人，於北平就學，對唱歌甚有研究，最令人有印象的他就是他那説得不清不楚的廣東鄉巴音。後赴港，曾於荔園遊樂場賣唱維生。\n\n1965 年，正式加入邵氏公司擔任基本演員，拍過一百多部影片，為著名的性格演員，演技老辣，令人折服，代表作有《新獨臂刀》、《保鑣》、《雙俠》及《清宮大刺殺》等，常以首領人物的姿態出現在電影中。他曾以《武松》一片獲第十九屆台灣金馬獎最佳男配角獎。一年後他再憑《待罪的女孩》衞冕同一個殊榮。另外《又見冤家》獲得了金馬獎最佳男配角獎提名；影片《籠民》更是引起影壇的轟動；另外在周星馳影片中的客串也是深入人心。近年來，谷峰以拍電視劇為主，但在電影《妖夜迴廊》仍可見其精採演出，也客串了《寶貝計畫》中成龍的父親。2025 年 3 月 27 日下午 4 時 30 分，谷峰被家人發現於家中離世，享耆壽 94 歲。","name":"谷峰","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Cốc Phong","primary":false}}]}},"tv_4629_keywords":{"at":1772691644931,"data":{"id":4629,"results":[{"name":"wormhole","id":3417},{"name":"space travel","id":3801},{"name":"space","id":9882},{"name":"travel","id":9935},{"name":"alien","id":9951},{"name":"alien planet","id":10158},{"name":"military","id":162365},{"name":"distant  planet","id":210591},{"name":"secret military program","id":210592},{"name":"advanced ancient civilization","id":350404}]}}}}